What's in a name? Great atmosphere, fairly priced drinks & a fun loving bar staff is what makes Filthy's a great destination for your next adventure. Daily drink specials and pizza served til 2am, Filthy's is sure to provide a unique party experience for everyone. Young or young at heart!
​
No reservations needed, but if you have a large party please give us a heads up to ensure the best attention is given to your group.
